description: Come see this beautiful new listing in the gated Kensington Park Villas Community! You will fall in love with this quaint, tree lined community and fully remodeled 3 bed plus a den 2 bathroom home. Walk into the front door and be sure not to pass by the secret room hidden behind a bookcase, set up as your very own speakeasy. This room could also serve as a great den, office or game room. Through this room you will access the large patio/ yard space. As you head up the stairs you will find the kitchen, living and dining area with beautiful upgrades and the integrity of the mid century modern lines, including large vaulted ceilings. The 3 bedrooms and bathrooms are separated from the living area for added privacy. The grounds of this community are stunning with koi ponds walking paths and even stairs to access the Kensington neighborhood. There is also a pool, spa and club house for your use.
